# Animated Text Demo - Pulse, Wave, Rainbow, Gradient, Sparkle effects
Source demos/settings.tape
Output demos/gifs/animated_text.gif

Hide
Type "cargo run --example animated_text_demo"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Show

# Watch animations run
Sleep 2s

# Navigate through effects
Down
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 1s

# Pause animations
Space
Sleep 1s

# Resume
Space
Sleep 2s

Type "q"
